{"tid":1478774,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"侵習準備會面，呢個時候點解要大大聲講攬炒？","createTime":"2019-08-16T15:53:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T00:15:16.000Z","uid":111806,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6155e22959360838ffb7e339b5ad413dec9d5bcf","tid":1478774,"uid":111806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:53:27.000Z","msg":"香港一直係中美管治，依家兩個元首準備會面傾香港問題<br />\n點解呢個時候點解要大大聲講攬炒？<br />\n香港係有機會贏（美國可能會令香港有普選），又唔係輸緊<br />\n攬炒係人都知，但呢個時候講會唔會令義士嘅仇恨度更高，令到第時會令雙方有更大嘅傷亡？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家侵習準備會面, 呢段時間應該要萬事小心，唔好衝動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7930f8277fbb918671bca409aba701982d3d54d9","tid":1478774,"uid":111806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:13:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9636fc71b98fe368568300cc131cd05aceeb5f5c","tid":1478774,"uid":206594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:24:59.000Z","msg":"點解唔嗌得<br />\n你都可以大嗌更加爆嘅口號"},{"pid":"c92bac75b3c11cfc90e70fca67815b5e4f9387ac","tid":1478774,"uid":111806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9636fc71b98fe368568300cc131cd05aceeb5f5c","tid":1478774,"uid":206594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:24:59.000Z","msg":"點解唔嗌得<br />\n你都可以大嗌更加爆嘅口號"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:31:25.000Z","msg":"怕會有義士嘅仇恨度更高，令到第時會令雙方有更大嘅傷亡"},{"pid":"291f0022dc73d232226750723cd4325fc0347a46","tid":1478774,"uid":206594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c92bac75b3c11cfc90e70fca67815b5e4f9387ac","tid":1478774,"uid":111806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9636fc71b98fe368568300cc131cd05aceeb5f5c","tid":1478774,"uid":206594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:24:59.000Z","msg":"點解唔嗌得<br />\n你都可以大嗌更加爆嘅口號"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:31:25.000Z","msg":"怕會有義士嘅仇恨度更高，令到第時會令雙方有更大嘅傷亡"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:35:08.000Z","msg"